    'date': {
        'plugins': ['TextPlugin', 'LinkPlugin'],
        'default_plugins':[
            {
                'plugin_type':'TextPlugin',
                'values':{
                    'body':'<p>January 13</p>'
                },
            },
        ]
    },

![screen shot 2018-12-21 at 12 38 51 pm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7341054/50355662-76fd1a00-051d-11e9-80f9-57fdfb89bfb9.png)

Hello all,
ckeditor removes empty tags (e.g.   <i class="fa fa-li></i> )  and i dont want that behavior.
I want to set something like  
```
    $.each(CKEDITOR.dtd.$removeEmpty, function (i, value) {
            CKEDITOR.dtd.$removeEmpty[i] = 0;
        }); 
```
but dont know how to set  inside settings.py
Is there some solution?
Hanz
